    <div class="into-beds__heading">
      <h2 class="title title--md">What goes into our beds</h2>
      <div class="text-container">
        <p>Every material and component is chosen to add comfort and quality to our beds and mattresses. Whether it’s finding the fleeciest alpaca hair or studying the best way to hand-tuft a mattress – we go to great lengths to help you sleep properly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="into-beds__container">
    <div class="into-beds__content">
      <div class="into-beds__image-wrapper">
        <div class="swiper-container" id="into-beds-image-slider">
          <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            <div class="swiper-slide">
              <div class="into-beds__image">
                <img data-lazy-src="/img/42.jpg" alt="beds image">
              </div>
